{"name": "odoo12-addon-hr-expense-payment-difference", "metadata": {"name": "odoo12-addon-hr-expense-payment-difference", "version": "12.0.1.1.0", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/hr", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Payment Difference on HR expenses", "upload_time": 1610432741}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fhr-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/hr\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/hr/tree/12.0/hr_expense_payment_difference\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/hr-12-0/hr-12-0-hr_expense_payment_difference\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runbot-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runbot\n    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/116/12.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Payment Difference on HR expenses\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module extend the functionality of payment wizard in hr expense,\nto also allow you to enter the payment difference amount.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n1. Go to Expenses > My Expenses\n2. Create a new Expense and Report as normal\n3. As normal, do Submit to Manager > Approve > Post Journal Entries > Register Payment.\n4. When you change Payment Amount not equal Total Amount, you will see new field \"Payment difference\".\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/hr/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/hr/issues/new?body=module:%20hr_expense_payment_difference%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Ecosoft\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Saran Lim. \\<<mailto:saranl@ecosoft.co.th>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/hr](https://github.com/OCA/hr/tree/12.0/hr_expense_payment_difference) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.hr_expense_payment_difference.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.hr_expense_payment_difference.models.account_payment", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.hr_expense_payment_difference.models..account_payment", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_expense_payment_difference.mo